# KRAKEN

Exchange plugin for bt_api framework.

[![PyPI Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/bt_api_kraken.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/bt_api_kraken/)
[![Python Versions](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/bt_api_kraken.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/bt_api_kraken/)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-blue.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)
[![CI](https://github.com/cloudQuant/bt_api_kraken/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/cloudQuant/bt_api_kraken/actions)
[![Docs](https://readthedocs.org/projects/bt-api-kraken/badge/?version=latest)](https://bt-api-kraken.readthedocs.io/)

