## English | [中文](#中文)

### Overview

This package provides **Kraken exchange plugin for bt_api** for the [bt_api](https://github.com/cloudQuant/bt_api_py) framework. It offers a unified interface for interacting with **KRAKEN** exchange.

### Features

- Exchange integration with bt_api
- REST API support
- Market data access
- Basic trading operations

### Installation

```bash
pip install bt_api_kraken
```

Or install from source:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/cloudQuant/bt_api_kraken
cd bt_api_kraken
pip install -e .
```

### Quick Start

```python
from bt_api_py import BtApi

# Initialize
api = BtApi(
    exchange_kwargs={
        "KRAKEN___SPOT": {
            "api_key": "your_key",
            "secret": "your_secret",
        }
    }
)

# Get ticker data
ticker = api.get_tick("KRAKEN___SPOT", "BTCUSDT")
print(ticker)
```

### Supported Operations

| Operation | Status |
|-----------|--------|
| Ticker | ✅ |
| OrderBook | ✅ |
| Trades | ✅ |
| Bars/Klines | ✅ |
| Orders | ✅ |
| Balances | ✅ |
| Positions | ✅ |

